text: Omo-Love Branch (born 10 January 1974) is a former defender. She played for the Nigeria women's national football team. She played in the 1991 FIFA Women's World Cup and the 1995 FIFA Women's World Cup. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Nigerian footballers Category:1991 FIFA Women's World Cup players Category:1995 FIFA Women's World Cup players Category:Association football defenders
